- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automatic speech translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech data and its processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses data augmentation and pretraining approaches for improving the performance of end-to-end AST models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with machine translation and speech recognition, which are both subfields of AI. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
